{"tid":214184,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(打大佬)印度貧民窟義診之旅","createTime":"2017-04-23T15:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T07:42:06.000Z","uid":110155,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aee7ce18108d9f675dbebe1f13c8a3e72e148031","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"大家好，幾經辛苦終於揾返個ISP EMAIL，正式過檔連登，即刻開個POST同大家分享下之前嘅行程！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家之前有睇過我啲POST，就知我係徒步撚，不過今次，我反而走左去印度義診，雖然9日印度行程入面，義診只有3日，但幫得幾多得幾多啦。<br />\n<br />\n點解我會去義診？因為我今次個旅伴係準醫生，所以去旅行之餘，想帶多少少野俾當地嘅人，所以我就經其他旅行朋友，揾到一個係Jaipur服務貧民窟嘅NGO，由聯絡同策略，一手一腳叫做搞左個義診行程出黎。<br />\n<br />\n其實義診嘅內容好簡單，只係量下血糖同血壓，但重點係，我係香港自費買左500-600張血糖試紙同血糖機，同埋有網友捐左佢個血壓計俾我，由我帶過去送俾佢地，教佢地點用，希望佢之後可以自己繼續做檢查。<br />\n<br />\n係到要再多謝香港嘅網友，捐左極多文具俾我帶過去，大約30公斤，因為真係帶唔到咁多，所以有啲會留返係我屋企，遲啲去其他地方再帶俾有需要嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，遊記開始！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9i74pt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9i74pt.jpg&h=2b9a19ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9C6041E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9C6041E.jpg&h=ba2810eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8jt1Df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8jt1Df.jpg&h=4fa790c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B826827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB826827.jpg&h=6435e0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2nTeCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2nTeCU.jpg&h=b44e9105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WS4smpb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWS4smpb.jpg&h=95a35c60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2f53b3034da676c3d62c347fab028f714f0709a","tid":214184,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:46:01.000Z","msg":"高質劉明"},{"pid":"46a206e7845a2af3628aa3842fdf3f7758c2f97b","tid":214184,"uid":52195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:51:59.000Z","msg":"睇圖樓主好似用手動血壓計，要用聽筒聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買個電子既快d準d，同埋比當地人學都易d"},{"pid":"a0d6d3cc38823fd8416688ca234ee8ace41b2c72","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"我去BACKPACK旅行，話多唔多話少唔少，由三年前由廣州搭順風車去拉薩加尼泊爾，再到徒步環台，澳洲WH，到上年徒步4256公里由墨西哥邊境穿越美國到加拿大，但係心目中一直都當印度係最終大佬，希望自己準備好啲先去印度，但結果都唔知那年那月先會去。<br />\n<br />\n咁啱同旅伴S小姐揾地方去，又咁啱決定做義工，又又咁啱朋友介紹印度嘅NGO，所以就決定今次去打大佬，睇下印度係咁真係咁得人驚....<br />\n<br />\n我地由新加坡轉機去到JAIPUR已經係零晨1點，係印度揾車最驚就係講價，但原來係印度已經可以用UBER叫車，個價分分鐘平過你自己三輪車，而且明碼實價，感覺安全好多，所以我地就叫車，先同NGO負責人會面，拿拿聲瞓覺第二日正常開始義診！<br />\n<br />\n第二日我地黎到JAIPUR西面一個貧民窟區域，今日嘅任務主要係留係NGO到等人黎講檢查，本來都好擔心無人黎，話說個活動係我發起，點都想幫多啲人，結果佢地一傳十十傳百，超多人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開始之前，見到NGO義工教當地小朋友識字同唱歌，好WARM，NGO大哥話，依到有未來嘅警察，工程師，數學家，個下真係好希望佢地可以一路接受教育，做到佢地想做嘅野...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i515p7L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi515p7L.jpg&h=79f9f899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Ow000r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Ow000r.jpg&h=55f4873f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9i74pt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9i74pt.jpg&h=2b9a19ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L68BL5g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL68BL5g.jpg&h=3f61cb33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2aa671dba081232a1d55a4c7cd9963aaed0c3c5","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇圖樓主好似用手動血壓計，要用聽筒聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買個電子既快d準d，同埋比當地人學都易d</blockquote><br />\n因為網友捐，所以自己慳返，其實手動血壓計係準過電子，同埋我唔知佢地個到會唔會停電，所以都係手動好啲"},{"pid":"7b78795b6ce7a182b1e04afcb1221052182bf0e8","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"睇佢地上完堂，終於黎到義診啦！<br />\n<br />\n我問問NGO大哥，先知原來今日得我地三個做野！(本來佢話有幫手)，S小姐負責血糖，NGO大哥負責紀錄佢地資料同溝通，而我，要即場學點用手動血壓計，即場幫佢地檢查....之前因為太忙無學過，再加上我一路都以為我只係負責影相，所以當場有啲手忙腳亂....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82as8Z2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82as8Z2.jpg&h=2593ff8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jEmejq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jEmejq.jpg&h=7e918dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81OAMwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81OAMwj.jpg&h=fc42aa21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4R6P555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4R6P555.jpg&h=2ae92275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G161xj5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG161xj5.jpg&h=582b4934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實義診無咩好講，如果大家期望有咩神奇故仔，咁我可以話要令大家失望啦，不過其實我當時個心情有啲矛盾，做得義診就當然唔希望佢地任何一個人有咩事啦，但如果佢地一個人都無事，又好似自己無做過野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後，當日我地只做左2-3個鐘就搞掂，我同左60個印度婦女做血壓檢查，有高血壓嘅唔多，但講真，就算真係查到有人有高血壓，咁又可以點，我地資源有限，無可能提供到藥俾佢地，只能同佢地講下有咩要注意嘅地方....."},{"pid":"d0a95a2981116445fd8e27056153602ac2cef9e2","tid":214184,"uid":32899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bbd7329bacab9da9e71ad7d99c6deed6c64acd","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"FACEBOOK：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WalkThruThePlanet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWalkThruThePlanet%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2FwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=94b9a9b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WalkThruThePlanet/</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅話請多多支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537e4c39625b6ac5fa8d7791646da8c37f8c3c11","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"做完義診，就係旅遊時間，去得JAIPUR，當然要去好出名嘅風之宮殿打卡啦。<br />\n<br />\n由於NGO大哥放我地係大街到，我見GOOGLE話我個個位置行過去大約30分鐘，我就同S小姐行過去，順便睇下市井嘅嘅印度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61249ig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61249ig.jpg&h=02ec28da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJAIPUR最大嘅戲院<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dj9i9DV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdj9i9DV.jpg&h=d2abad02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5902X56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5902X56.jpg&h=13cfa4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8Zo645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8Zo645.jpg&h=d76b0aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCPr2P7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCPr2P7.jpg&h=e4949b7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vdZ7294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvdZ7294.jpg&h=b157691a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05728N8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05728N8.jpg&h=cfd5d197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/962t2X6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F962t2X6.jpg&h=a7655fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wM57fWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwM57fWU.jpg&h=7a6ae629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZc7131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZc7131.jpg&h=f631001d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R826MF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR826MF4.jpg&h=31270774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Rc47V5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Rc47V5.jpg&h=7346a254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WS4smpb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWS4smpb.jpg&h=95a35c60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話時話，都幾佩服S小姐肯陪我行依30分鐘，因為今次係佢第一次BACKPACK，就黎左印度....."},{"pid":"e7eb87272230ab6ce0391a4eda526cd871c83993","tid":214184,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:20:24.000Z","msg":"全身而退？"},{"pid":"db0bd7f8870aaf200a2d6d88d615e0fa92880264","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"黎到city palace，好多介紹都話必去，但老實講，入到去覺得好一般，如果大家對JAIPUR嘅歷史有興趣，都可以去睇下，入場費500盧比...好貴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/558x35Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F558x35Y.jpg&h=9b52673a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p78ecZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp78ecZ8.jpg&h=7df9aa39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S39kSJk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS39kSJk.jpg&h=da0ccea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SUkeThq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSUkeThq.jpg&h=558cb800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2h53EM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2h53EM.jpg&h=c22ac932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後黎到風之宮殿，我唸大家都知，係外面打卡就夠，入面聽講反而無野睇，而我地因為唔趕行程，所以係宮殿對面屋頂嘅CAFE到飲野，HEA左幾個鐘....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3c2q5Y1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3c2q5Y1.jpg&h=efc2ab3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OC301n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OC301n.jpg&h=7a593d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tMaf51N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtMaf51N.jpg&h=dccd487d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2nTeCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2nTeCU.jpg&h=b44e9105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cf31w30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcf31w30.jpg&h=07a35a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇住日落後佢慢慢變色都幾正！<br />\n<br />\n我地係CAFE到，基本上試晒印度嘅特色飲品，大家最好叫少糖，唔係實甜死你...."},{"pid":"9213cd987832244b8f15db5cfae69bd4d7882a1b","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全身而退？</blockquote><br />\n無穿無爛"},{"pid":"b2c6ed757552cc337f20954324dd288cef9525ce","tid":214184,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"d街都好乾淨下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeda0a08313ca1c04cc50fcd9b3826a8a2dacac1","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d街都好乾淨下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都算OK，有時有啲牛屎好正常，仲有間唔中有男人對住牆屙尿....<br />\n<br />\n不過大塵到仆街係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d24c0d34a11bb2f5a72dda04507ce1fc12ee4b","tid":214184,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"依架覺得NGO好似有d騙子感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4208bb305942798303c198a10fc6d891a3ded6","tid":214184,"uid":74041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c9fb9b7b6ce791b72c25a86fe408bcea0e0dfa8d","tid":214184,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"自問無咁嘅心機去幫人<br />\n但我一路都覺得只要每人做少少咁多<br />\n個世界都可以和平啲<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b095cdd57f996c83f4debe4d9c720e3773fcb55c","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依架覺得NGO好似有d騙子感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼我依個無，佢自己之前有全職，之後唔做份工，拎自己錢黎租地方，去教貧民窟小朋友，同埋揾人教婦女成衣類嘅技術"},{"pid":"4ef6e74da7edd5dbcd5ac60753df80dd7072d850","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自問無咁嘅心機去幫人<br />\n但我一路都覺得只要每人做少少咁多<br />\n個世界都可以和平啲<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁唸，其實我真係唔CARE去左幾多個景點，最緊要係自己有咩得着，咁去幫下人，自己又學到野，WHY NOT"},{"pid":"d224406084912d3171e6f9a39453f132f60e3e39","tid":214184,"uid":14341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:33:04.000Z","msg":"個NGO大哥講既野好warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印度建築真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想去但唔夠膽去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3e852a289858c9e1aafe9f6c8abc6aa57a3de5","tid":214184,"uid":27293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:34:02.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d640703a5752656db8b78256241ecc6d208407a","tid":214184,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T18:15:22.000Z","msg":"有d好奇接受過義診既人會點樣回報你, 會唔會請你食咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8110fa888d271d2e5576010a85c655e2c431827","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T18:31:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d好奇接受過義診既人會點樣回報你, 會唔會請你食咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會，咁小事，檢查下姐。。。<br />\n<br />\n同埋真係不求回報，個行程學到野，體驗到啲野已經係回報"},{"pid":"c24b3c104783f65a8ccb6f95a6220850290cf654","tid":214184,"uid":110118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:20:10.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b126281af5c34443b3688f0859beea525601de8f","tid":214184,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"Hollister<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0531f2369d82de202dec7271b344eab86e5bd29a","tid":214184,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:25:43.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41e7575704b51b9166841be2f11b45202d95ee8","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"第二日繼續義診，今日換左另一個地點，不過都係NGO大哥自己自費租黎教學嘅房，因為今日有人黎幫手，所以我可以齋影相唔洗做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdU67N9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdU67N9.jpg&h=40751d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/155FTHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F155FTHK.jpg&h=6a048408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJd044C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJd044C.jpg&h=974615f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/STD6xM8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSTD6xM8.jpg&h=a836635d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3843h3F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3843h3F.jpg&h=43aab86a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3M8Agx6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3M8Agx6.jpg&h=46a98689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1vTzk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1vTzk5.jpg&h=c74ae1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPGF4W5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPGF4W5.jpg&h=592ec402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾有個大媽，上壓去到200，嚇到S小姐要重做多幾次去肯定有無度錯，原來佢本身就知自己有高血壓，平時都有食開藥，但今日唔記得食，結果即刻爆晒標.....我地要警告佢下次唔好唔記得食藥，俾佢知道個嚴重.....<br />\n<br />\n過程期間有好多細佬黎睇野，NGO大哥就會同我講佢地細細個就去個中心，到宜家都大個仔晒，所以NGO大哥同貧民窟啲人好FD"},{"pid":"7c669103b5d416344a010ad256e4166cf78089fa","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:23:39.000Z","msg":"完左義診第二日，我地先坐車到郊區的Jaigarh Fort，依到名氣雖然唔及旁邊嘅Amber Fort大，但勝在門票平啲，人流少啲，可以感受一下係印度難得嘅寧靜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4A7Vgk9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4A7Vgk9.jpg&h=00eab793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44R3O95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44R