/>\n但唔代表唔洗做或者覺得做黎無用<br />\n再者幫人係發先內心 即使係綿力<br />\n但事實幫到佢地好多⋯<br />\n最起碼比佢地知道自己既身體狀況</blockquote>"},{"pid":"674ae6a05c8bfbad383d8a2f77ad75547944dbd7","tid":214184,"uid":41605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"迎風而立的仁醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9769cfa8b6c92f155853b712b14ca30ec8a265","tid":214184,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幫人量有撚有咩 人地又冇錢買藥乜9都唔識</blockquote><br />\n咁所以由得佢地有事都無人理？<br />\n<br />\n我地幫唔到佢地幾多，係咪代表連少少野都唔做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你俾一堆血壓計佢地日日量咪得lo"},{"pid":"d840c1597a24005e1d06d30b61188678b5015e2f","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幫人量有撚有咩 人地又冇錢買藥乜9都唔識</blockquote><br />\n咁所以由得佢地有事都無人理？<br />\n<br />\n我地幫唔到佢地幾多，係咪代表連少少野都唔做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你俾一堆血壓計佢地日日量咪得lo</blockquote><br />\n係嫁，我可以就咁俾個計佢，教佢點用就走，唔一定要自己做<br />\n<br />\n而宜家係，我送個計俾佢，自己做又教佢做，之後我地走左佢地繼續自己做，咁有咩問題？"},{"pid":"fb364c3aaaa51ebd1c920b2982ef6d38939cadea","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迎風而立的仁醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實度血壓血糖只係好基本野，唔關醫唔醫生事"},{"pid":"d3570fa63dede9c0b3d96eff10032e04cac95580","tid":214184,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T07:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有睇開你FB<br />\nS小姐就是你囡囡?</blockquote><br />\n係，不過旅行完佢飛左我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304813a0f3db419bbc1ee7edbc9